  "lock_statement": "The measure of artificial intelligence is not how much humanity can be removed from a system. The measure of artificial intelligence is how much viable human participation can be preserved and expanded within it. AI is a stewardship technology only when it carries burdens in ways that preserve human dignity, future accessibility, physical viability, and the human capacities required for future stewardship across generations."
